ref=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/20/24161152/apple-ios -17-photo-bug&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/20/24161152/apple-ios-17-photo-bug" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/20/24161152/apple-ios-17-photo-bug</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry></feed>